snippet.title: Why We Need A Change
snippet.description:
New Smiths episodes launch every Tuesday and Thursday at 6pm CST!
New Arise With Amber episodes launch every Sunday at 8am CST!
Yee Yee Apparel ►  https://YeeYeeApparel.com/
Watch "That's Why I Love Dirt Roads" Music Video here ► https://youtu.be/UvlWF4g8XA0
Listen to my new song here► https://grangersmith.lnk.to/dirtroads
Tickets to Granger's Tour► https://GrangerSmith.com/tour
Watch new Granger Smith Music Vlog here► https://youtu.be/JcYSWg4-zKM
Visit the River Kelly Fund Website here► https://www.riverkellyfund.org/

PO Box if you'd like to send us or the kids something:
The Smiths
4500 Williams Drive
Ste 212 - PMP 304
Georgetown, TX 78633

Our Other Youtube Channels:
Granger's Music Channel► https://youtube.com/GrangerSmithMusic
Yee Yee Life► https://youtube.com/yeeyeelife

TALK TO US ON SOCIAL MEDIA :
GRANGER'S:
Instagram► https://instagram.com/GrangerSmith
Facebook► https://facebook.com/GrangerSmith
Twitter► https://twitter.com/GrangerSmith
AMBER'S:
Instagram► https://instagram.com/amberemilysmith

AMBER'S Amazon ► www.amazon.com/shop/amberemilysmith
AMBER'S ETSY ► https://etsy.me/2CHdZFH

About this channel: We are the Smith's. A family of 5, living in the country just outside of Georgetown, Texas. Granger, a touring country music singer, Amber, an actor and stay at home mom, and their children: London, Lincoln and River.
